{"sections":{"ss_text_block_C7YxXY":{"type":"ss-text-block","blocks":{"text_FFxFHU":{"type":"text","settings":{"heading":"<h1><strong>Welcome to Learning SPACE <\/strong><\/h1><h1><strong>Transforming Spaces with Thoughtful Design and Functionality<\/strong><\/h1><h5>At Learning SPACE, we understand the unique needs of healthcare and commercial settings. Whether you’re creating a welcoming reception area, a comfortable waiting room, or a functional workspace, we provide tailored solutions that seamlessly combine aesthetics, durability, and practicality.<\/h5><h3><\/h3>","color":"#121212","font_size":36,"richtext":"","richtext_color":"#121212","richtext_font_size":14}}},"block_order":["text_FFxFHU"],"custom_css":[],"settings":{"padding_header":10,"padding_button":10,"background-color":"#ffffff","padding_top":32,"padding_bottom":0,"section-width":120}},"main":{"type":"page","disabled":true,"settings":{}},"ss_feature_1_x4byhd":{"type":"ss-feature-1","blocks":{"image_DMEWhj":{"type":"image","settings":{"feature_title":"Designed for Comfort and Well-being","feature_text":"<p>In healthcare environments, patient comfort is paramount. Our ergonomic furniture and thoughtfully designed spaces promote relaxation and reduce stress, helping to create a healing atmosphere. For commercial settings, we prioritize functionality and comfort to enhance productivity and employee satisfaction.<\/p>","feature_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/relaxation-icon-vector-outline-editable-600nw-2391054601.webp","feature_url":"https:\/\/section.store\/","hide_image":false}},"image_dB3acQ":{"type":"image","settings":{"feature_title":"Durable and Hygienic Materials","feature_text":"<p>We know that high-traffic areas require robust, easy-to-maintain furnishings. Our products are made from premium materials that are built to last and designed to meet hygiene standards, making them ideal for healthcare and commercial spaces alike<\/p>","feature_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/istockphoto-1215529139-6